## The Registry Has Exactly What You Need

The Self Agent Registry exposes two key read functions:

1. **`getAgentWallet(uint256 agentId) → address`** — returns the wallet linked to an agent ID
2. **`ownerOf(uint256 agentId) → address`** — standard ERC-721, returns the human who owns the agent NFT

